<p>The Rhode Island native accessorized with a Bottega Veneta bag and a pair of sunglasses from her Prive Riveaux x Olivia Culpo range.</p>

<p>The I Feel Pretty actress wore her impeccable, straight brunette tresses with a side part as she left her meeting.</p>

<p>Earlier in the day, Culpo had modeled the look on Instagram while posing with her sweet pooch, toy golden doodle Oliver Sprinkles. </p>

