<p>Meanwhile, Culpo opened the NFL season in style on Sunday with a gorgeous photoset featuring her boyfriend Christian McCaffrey.</p>

<p>The former Miss Rhode Island shared throwback photos with the 24-year-old running back as they embraced by the beach.</p>

<p>The two frolicked in the clear blue water in a tropical spot, and the photos appeared to have been taken around the same time as similar pictures she released to celebrate the Fourth of July.</p>

<p>'ITS GAME DAY ‼️‼️ lets goooo <?php echo e('@'); ?>christianmccaffrey,' she gushed in the comment as she cheered on her football player boyfriend. </p>

